        public OlapDataSource getDataSource(ConnectionInfo connectionInfo)
        Description copied from interface: DataSourceManager
        Create an OLAP datasource from the specified connection information. Note that the returned OlapDataSource should be able to serve multiple connections, so returning a SingleConnectionDataSource instance would cause an error for certain operations.
